## Quick Start

### 1. Configure IPP Printer

```python
from backend.print_pipeline import submit_ipp_job

job = submit_ipp_job(
    printer_uri="ipp://printer.local/ipp/print",
    document_format="application/pdf",
    attributes={"copies": 2, "sides": "two-sided-long-edge"},
)
```

### 2. Generate PCL Output

```python
from backend.print_pipeline import generate_pcl

pcl = generate_pcl(
    page_size="a4",
    resolution_dpi=600,
    duplex="duplex_long",
    pages=3,
)
# pcl.data contains the PCL byte stream
```

### 3. Select ICC Profile

```python
from backend.print_pipeline import select_print_profile

profile = select_print_profile(paper_id="paper_glossy", ink_id="cmyk_photo")
# profile.icc_file = "glossy_cmyk_photo.icc"
# profile.rendering_intent = "perceptual"
```

### 4. Enqueue Print Job

```python
from backend.print_pipeline import enqueue_print_job, advance_queue_job_to_completion

job = enqueue_print_job(
    document_name="report.pdf",
    printer_uri="ipp://printer.local/ipp/print",
    priority=75,
)
advance_queue_job_to_completion(job.job_id)
```

